7.text: Amitha: Wow! Did you do it all by yourself?

8.text: Milan: All by myself? How could I? Ameena and Romesh helped me with the invitations for the invitees and the judges. Our art teacher himself designed the invitation for the Chief Guest.

9.text: Saranga: Rajeshwari, how about selecting costumes for the drama, the sound system and the decorations?

10.text: Rajeshwari: Jude will take care of the sounds. Ruvin and Meena

11.text: promised to do the decorations by themselves. But, selecting costumes for the drama is a problem. I can’t manage it by myself. I need someone to help me.

16.text: Saranga: Our English teacher said that she herself would prepare them. Well, we seem to be doing fine so far. I’m sure we can make the English camp a success and be proud of ourselves.
